es.csic.iiia.nsm.strategy.iron.generalisation
Class GeneralisationTrees

java.lang.Object
  es.csic.iiia.nsm.strategy.iron.generalisation.GeneralisationTrees

public class GeneralisationTrees
extends java.lang.Object

Class containing the potential generalisation of each norm in the normative network. Every time the NSM generates a new norm, it computes its potential generalisations and adds them to this data structure. Then, the IRON strategy continuously checks along time if any potential generalisation may be performed. Whenever a potential generalisation fulfils the conditions to be performed, the NSM generalises norms as follows:

  1. it retrieves the potential parent from the potential generalisation;
  2. it adds the parent norm to the normative network and activates it;
  3. it deactivates the child norms in the normative network; and
  4. it sets the potential generalisation as "performed".

Author:
"Javier Morales (jmorales@iiia.csic.es)"
